snippet.title: Kyle & April - Ride MTB
snippet.description:
This channel is here to help people get stoked and learn more about Mountain Biking!      More Below ...

My name is Kyle Warner and i was born and raised in Chico, Ca. and during highschool my mom was very sick and my brother was battling addiction, I needed an escape and found biking. I was able to channel that pain into positive energy and have been a professional for the last 10 years. I hope to pass along some of the things I have learned to you guys! 
&
My name is April Zastrow and I was raised in Boise, Id and i'm newer to MTB, however i have some crossover from my career as a pro motocross racer. I am always pushing to improve and I love inspiring people to try new things.

We really want to help people embrace the sport and feel welcome. Hopefully we can help make your riding experience a little more fun! Thanks for watching and don't be afraid to say hi on the trails!

Kyle & April 
Contact, Website - https://www.ridemtb.com/
Merchandise - https://shopridemtb.com/
